{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is maybe there might be, you know, 20 people stacked on top of one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They've quit stacking them now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're just in the hole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then bulldozing dirt on top.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they put a marker on each pit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There's 9 or 10 pits.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "An estimate of how many people are in there, and there's over 100,000 that I know of, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now I've read some books about-- Bergen-Belsen is-- is-- there's not too much about that American-- in English for some reason.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a couple of books that tell you, but I've read, uh, books about-- what's the guy's name that-- that wrote 'The Holocaust'?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've got several of his.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mitchell-- uh, Gilbert-- Martin Gilbert.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've corresponded with him, by the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was Churchill's historian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wonderful man.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's written probably 30 books about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were set-- they had set up field hospitals, and they were-- they had brought-- there was no water.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There had been no water to the camp for two weeks is what I was told.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here again there were warehouses with food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The SS, they had all-- they had captured 40, 50 SS, women included, and the commandant of the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his biggest complaint was that he-- the water in the river was so-- the river was so full of dead bodies that it was contaminated, and he couldn't use the water to water-- to provide water for the inmates.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were without water for a couple of weeks, without food for a couple weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody-- all the SS were healthy looking, fat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've got pictures of them, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All around this area were farms.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
